==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pavonine
<hw>Pav"o*nine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pavoninus</ets>, fr. <ets>pavo</ets> a peacock. See
<er>Peacock</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Like, or
pertaining to, the genus Pavo.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Characteristic of a peacock; resembling the tail of
a peacock, as in colors; iridescent.</def> <rj><au>P.
Cleaveland.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Paw</ent>⟦br⟧
